-## Sample Library V6 And Thumbnail Preview
-
-- Created rollback archive:
-  `Docs/Design/SampleLibraryArchive/2026-05-04-before-v6-sample-thumbnails-and-preview/`.
-- Made first-run utility samples more visually mixed: the Airbnb access save now
-  looks like a stay/access card, and the hotel booking save now looks like a
-  real confirmation card with dates, confirmation number, QR-style block, and
-  check-in details.
-- Strengthened AI prompt samples with actual reusable prompt text for turning
-  chaos into a plan, cross-checking blind spots, and finding recurring talents.
-- Added distinct AI prompt thumbnails for the new prompt examples instead of
-  leaving them as generic note cards.
-- Bumped the native sample seed version to `9` so empty/sample libraries can
-  refresh to the new V6 catalog while preserving personal saves.
-- Fixed item detail dead taps for sample notes/files that only have a thumbnail:
-  tapping the preview/title now opens a thumbnail image viewer when no URL or
-  saved asset exists, and the action panel shows `View Image` for those cases.
-
-## Sample Library V7 Visual Mix
-
-- Reused the V6 rollback archive and expanded its forward/revert patches to
-  cover the final V7 sample-visual pass.
-- Added custom note-style thumbnails for more text saves so launch content no
-  longer falls back to repeated generic placeholders:
-  dinner shopping list, gift ideas, packing list, reusable email, quote, quick
-  clipboard clip, recovery protocol, and protein snack list.
-- Added a custom video-style thumbnail for the `Goyo goyo with lyrics` sample
-  and the documentary save so the demo library has a better media/document/note
-  rhythm.
-- Bumped the native sample seed version to `10` so empty/sample libraries can
-  refresh into the V7 catalog while preserving personal saves.
